Class PaginatedData<T>

  • java.lang.Object

    T - 

    public class PaginatedData<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the paginated data record. e.g. there are 100 records in db and we have 10 pages, so the first page has 10 records. numberOfRows = 100 rows.size = 10 (first page 10 records)
